snippet.title: Hard Nova gameplay (PC Game, 1990)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Hard Nova, Dos PC game produced by Electronic Arts in 1990 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/hard-nova/1559/
Starting some missions for this role playing-action-simulation game where you are a space mercenary.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
